{"tid":2332794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"直擊日本宅男與初音結婚後生活 花200萬搞婚禮為初音訂雙人床 曾受女同事欺負失意時遇上初音 ：「她不會背叛我！」","createTime":"2020-12-20T01:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T02:57:01.000Z","uid":25345,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36812d1c2fc0d70e034154a49028280649048696","tid":2332794,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"東京愛的故事&mdash;我的虛擬老婆  直擊日宅男與初音婚後生活：「她不會背叛我！」<br />\n2018年尾，一則日本宅男與虛擬歌手初音未來的婚訊，轟動全世界。一年多過後，記者帶大家直擊他們的新婚生活。走到一個寧靜的住宅小區內，眼前一棟別致的藍色小屋，門牌上貼着近藤顯彥和初音未來。沒錯了，這便是他們的愛巢。<br />\n<br />\n在2018年，Gatebox公司進行了一個與心儀虛擬角色結婚的企劃。雖然沒法律效力，但近藤成了三千多名申請者的其中一名幸運兒，與初音踏入人生另一個階段。他說：「由08到18年，我喜歡上初音都接近10年了，我覺得自己對初音的感情不會有變，所以便選擇了更進一步。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xXXlpV7X3V4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxXXlpV7X3V4&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=a8f99a3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xXXlpV7X3V4</a>"},{"pid":"448faba5b00cfc501a350366e3acb2a63d4ec865","tid":2332794,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:54:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e988805df0c74979619ae443dae10b939119fb1","tid":2332794,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6375eac2ab6b1c6c0461b57e5888ebefeb827e9e","tid":2332794,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"要講幾多年"},{"pid":"751dd2f003bcb718f737da1821d261a974a28ab2","tid":2332794,"uid":142965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class